    "description": "<p>Established in 2014, Shanghai Geoharbour Construction Group Co. Ltd Singapore Branch serves as the regional hub of Geoharbour Group, overseeing multiple branches and subsidiaries across various regions. Geoharbour Group provides global customers with comprehensive geotechnical engineering services integrating survey, design, construction and monitoring, mainly including foundation treatment and pile foundation engineering. The company's engineering performance covers China, Southeast Asia, the Middle East, South Asia, Latin America and other regions, involving airports, ports, highways, railways, power plants, municipal administration, petrochemical industry, national defense engineering, and land reclamation from the sea.&nbsp;</p>",
